<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dépôt de CV — GICAT × Entreprise partenaire</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #f4f1f9;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: #190038;
  }

  .hero {
    background: #190038;
    padding: 32px 20px 28px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .schools {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .school-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .school-sep {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #6b3a9e;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #fbb908;
    color: #190038;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.45;
    max-width: 340px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px 16px 40px;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #5a5a7a;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .campus-block {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e0d9ee;
    border-radius: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .campus-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 15px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .campus-header:hover {
    background: #f9f7fd;
  }

  .campus-header:active {
    background: #f0ecf9;
  }

  .campus-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .campus-pin {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    background: #190038;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .campus-pin svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    fill: none;
    stroke: #fbb908;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .campus-name {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #190038;
  }

  .chevron {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
    color: #9b89bf;
  }

  .chevron svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .chevron.open {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .campus-body {
    display: none;
    background: #f9f7fd;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e2f4;
    padding: 12px 12px 14px;
  }

  .campus-body.open {
    display: block;
  }

  .spec-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 7px;
  }

  .spec-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e0d9ee;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 11px 13px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #190038;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  .spec-btn:hover {
    background: #190038;
    color: #fbb908;
    border-color: #190038;
  }

  .spec-btn:hover .spec-icon {
    color: #fbb908;
  }

  .spec-btn:hover .spec-arrow {
    color: #fbb908;
  }

  .spec-icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #4a0a6c;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .spec-icon svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .spec-label {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .spec-arrow {
    color: #fbb908;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .spec-arrow svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .footer {
    background: #190038;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer p {
    color: #c9b8e8;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 40px 24px 36px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 22px; max-width: 460px; }
    .spec-btn { font-size: 14px; }
    .spec-label { font-size: 14px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="schools">
    <span class="school-name">INSEEC</span>
    <span class="school-sep">×</span>
    <span class="school-name">Sup de Pub</span>
    <span class="school-sep">×</span>
    <span class="school-name">HEIP</span>
    <span class="school-sep">×</span>
    <span class="school-name">ECE</span>
  </div>
  <div class="badge">Dépôt de CV — Entreprise partenaire</div>
  <h1>Rejoignez une base de données de 480 entreprises du secteur défense</h1>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <p class="intro">Sélectionne ton campus puis ta spécialité pour déposer ton CV directement dans la bonne Dropbox.</p>

  <div id="campuses"></div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>Une question ? Contacte le service relations entreprises.</p>
</div>

<script>
